parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of Carlisle tires can cause blowouts, leading to accidents, damage to the trailer, and potential harm to occupants.
The failure of Al-Ko axles can cause tire blowouts, leading to accidents, damage to the trailer, and potential harm to occupants.
The misrepresentation of tire specifications can lead to tire failure, accidents, and potential harm to occupants.
The failure of the travel trailer's frame can cause instability and loss of control while towing, leading to accidents or damage to the trailer and surrounding property.
symptoms: The trailer's tongue can be moved up and down excessively
indicating a loose or weakened frame.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire failure on a travel trailer can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Tires may rub against each other
leading to blowouts and tread separation; multiple tires may be affected.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Travel Trailer Gas Line and LP Gas System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gas line and LP gas system can cause gas leaks, fires, and explosions, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Soft copper tubing may be exposed and unprotected
and the LP gas system may turn on unexpectedly while towing

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical Wiring Failure in Recreational Vehicles
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of electrical wiring in recreational vehicles can cause fires, electrical shocks, and damage to appliances, posing a significant risk to the safety of occupants and bystanders.
symptoms: arcing or sparking of electrical connections.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Poor Electrical Design and Installation in Recreational Vehicles
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Poor electrical design and installation can lead to electrical failures, fires, and electrical shocks, posing a significant risk to the safety of occupants and bystanders.
symptoms: arcing or sparking of electrical connections
